Description
Booking
The Booking class represents a booking with an identifier, user ID, car ID, start date, and end date.
BookingDao
The BookingDao class provides methods for interacting with the "booking" table in the database.
BookingService
The BookingService class provides methods for managing booking-related operations.
BookingServlet
The BookingServlet class handles HTTP requests related to booking operations.
Car
The Car class represents a car with an identifier, model, and availability status.
CarDao
The CarDao class provides methods for interacting with the "car" table in the database.
CarService
The CarService class provides methods for managing car-related operations.
CarServlet
The CarServlet class handles HTTP requests related to car operations.
ConnectionPoolManager
The ConnectionPoolManager class is a utility class for managing a connection pool.
PropertiesManager
The PropertiesManager class is a utility class for managing properties loaded from "application.properties" file.
User
The User class represents a user with an identifier, username, password, and role.
UserDao
The UserDao class provides methods for interacting with the "user" table in the database.
UserRole
The UserRole enum class represents the roles of users, which can be either "User" or "Admin".
UserService
The UserService class provides methods for managing user-related operations.
UserServlet
The UserServlet class handles HTTP requests related to user operations.
